/* This is the Reversi version (aka dark mode), meant to be paired with the Reversi public skin.
To use this skin, add Reversi as a parent skin and then use this skin.
Or, if you want to use other skins in addition to this one, just create a new skin and add this skin, Reversi, and the other skins you want to use as parents of the skin.

DESCRIPTION:
- Alternates the color of forms from their text fields, sub fields, legends (the label at the top left), and the background of the page.
  This is based on the default Archive skin, just modified for Reversi's color scheme.
- Replaces the button styling on the Search text field (in the Navigation bar) with the text field styling of the Tag Search page.
  Subtly changes the bottom border color and the spacing of its margins to distinguish it from the background of the navigation bar.
  Also makes a minor improvement to how the navigation bar stacks on mobile (reduces the space between dropdown menu options and the Search section for more equal spacing).
 */


/* Header Search Field */
#header #search #site_search {
  box-shadow: inset 0 1px 2px #000;
  background: #333;
  border: 1px solid #222;
  border-bottom-color: #444;
  margin: 0.429em;
}

#header .primary a {
  padding-bottom: 0em;
}

/* Add background color variation to forms */
fieldset,
form dl,
